# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# TCPK .gitignore -- keep audit outputs and target apps OUT of the repo.
# Audit outputs can contain REAL secrets extracted from a target. Never commit.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------

# Audit output folders + artifacts (may contain real findings/secrets)
out/
**/out/
**/report.xlsx
**/findings.json
**/attack-surface.json
**/sbom.cdx.json
**/strings.json
**/exploits.json
**/profile.json
**/run.jsonl

# Target applications / extracted packages / binaries under test
*.msix
*.appx
*.msixbundle
*.appxbundle
WindowsApps/

# Crash / memory dumps and fuzzing output
*.dmp
tcpk-fuzz/

# Scratch + temp work dirs
_smoke*/
_audit*/
_logotest*/
_sbom*/
_extracted*/
*.tmp

# OS / editor noise
Thumbs.db
.DS_Store
*.swp
.vs/
.vscode/

# Local LLM config may hold an API key - never commit
**/llm-config.json
